  "detailed_description": "Bleeding Blocks is a 2D arena shooter. Two players face off in a single-screen deathmatch. Winning requires more than quick reflexes. Players must use cover and tactics to outsmart the enemy.<br><br>Choose from six unique classes. Will you rush in as the Rogue? Snipe from afar as the Reaper? Or deploy turrets as the Engineer? Play against a deviously smart AI or head to head in local multiplayer mode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 different classes.<br></li><li>Bullet-hell reflex shooting combined with tactical gameplay employing cover and flanking.<br></li><li>A devious AI capable of flanking and outsmarting human players.<br></li><li>Single and local multiplayer modes.<br></li><li>Catchy Synthwave music.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Bleeding Blocks is a 2D arena shooter. Two players face off in a single-screen deathmatch. Winning requires more than quick reflexes. Players must use cover and tactics to outsmart the enemy.<br><br>Choose from six unique classes. Will you rush in as the Rogue? Snipe from afar as the Reaper? Or deploy turrets as the Engineer? Play against a deviously smart AI or head to head in local multiplayer mode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 different classes.<br></li><li>Bullet-hell reflex shooting combined with tactical gameplay employing cover and flanking.<br></li><li>A devious AI capable of flanking and outsmarting human players.<br></li><li>Single and local multiplayer modes.<br></li><li>Catchy Synthwave music.</li></ul>",
